Package: deltaccd
Type: Package
Title: Quantify rhythmic gene co-expression relative to a reference
Version: 0.2.3
Authors@R: as.person(c(
  'Jake Hughey <jakejhughey@gmail.com> [aut, cre]',
  'Elliot Outland <ehoutland@gmail.com> [aut]'))
Description: deltaccd can infer progression of circadian rhythms in
  transcriptome data in which samples are not labeled with time of day and
  coverage of the circadian cycle may be incomplete.
URL: https://github.com/hugheylab/deltaccd
